      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A stack view uses this property to define the minimum distance between views within a gravity area and between neighboring views in adjacent gravity areas. The default value for the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488945-spacing"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property is "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "8.0"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " points. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The automatically applied Auto Layout constraints for "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488945-spacing"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " are shown in "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488945-spacing#1965587"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "header": "row",
          "rows": [
            [
              [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Constraint"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Value for constraint priority"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "inter-view spacing "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "codeVoice",
                      "code": "=="
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " the "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": false,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488945-spacing"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " property value"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "max (NSLayoutPriorityDefaultHigh, hugging priority)"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "inter-gravity-area spacing "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "codeVoice",
                      "code": "=="
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " the "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": false,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488945-spacing"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " property value"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "hugging priority"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            ],
            [
              [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "inter-view spacing "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "codeVoice",
                      "code": "≥"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " the "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "reference",
                      "isActive": false,
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488945-spacing"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " property value"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "NSLayoutPriorityRequired"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            ]
          ],
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "1965587",
            "title": "Table 1",
            "abstract": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Default Auto Layout constraints for view spacing"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The first row in "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488945-spacing#1965587"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " indicates that inter-view spacing is constrained to equal the value of the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488945-spacing"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property with a priority of at least "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nslayoutprioritydefaulthigh"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "; you can increase this by setting a higher stack view hugging priority with the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488904-sethuggingpriority"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The second row in "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488945-spacing#1965587"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " indicates that the spacing between adjacent views in neighboring gravity areas is constrained to equal the value of the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488945-spacing"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property with the priority of the stack view’s hugging priority."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The third row in "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488945-spacing#1965587"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " indicates that inter-view spacing is allowed to grow larger than the value of the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488945-spacing"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property with a priority of NSLayoutPriorityRequired."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "In combination, these constraints result in the following typical stack view behavior: In a stack view whose "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488957-hasequalspacing"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property is set to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/no"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (the default) and whose hugging priority is left at "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nslayoutprioritydefaultlow"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (the default), views within a gravity area remain a fixed distance from each other (equal to the value of the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488945-spacing"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property), and the distance between gravity areas grows and shrinks as the stack view grows and shrinks along its layout direction axis. If you set the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsstackview/1488957-hasequalspacing"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and use the default hugging priority, then the distance between all adjacent views, including adjacent views in neighboring gravity areas, grows and shrinks as the stack view grows and shrinks."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": []
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": []
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
